title: Incredible Townhome!!! LUXURY!!! WOW!!! MUST SEE!!!
posting_body: ['MUST HAVE STRONG CREDIT!', 'NO EVICTIONS!', 'NO CRIMINAL RECORDS!', 'NO EXCEPTIONS!', 'PLEASE FIND THE EXACT PROPERTY ADDRESS 1/4 INCH UNDER THE MAP IN THE LISTING FOR YOUR REFERENCE!!!!!', 'CALL NOW!!!!!', 'PLEASE FIND THE EXACT PROPERTY ADDRESS 1/4 INCH UNDER THE MAP IN THE LISTING FOR YOUR REFERENCE!!!!!!', 'Email Me, Call Me, or Text!!!!', 'Shawn Kaminsky', 'show contact info', 'LOCATED JUST MINUTES FROM ATLANTIC AVENUE!', 'Come and view this contemporary 3 bed / 2.5 bath townhome with double garage located in the sought-after gated community of Coastal Bay in Boynton Beach.', 'This spacious home welcomes you into a large open plan living area with laminate flooring, crown molding, recessed lighting, crystal light fixtures, designated formal dining space and upgraded eat-in kitchen with wood cabinetry, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, double sink, high top snack bar and breakfast nook.', 'Sliding doors lead to your own private landscaped backyard - the ideal spot to enjoy the FL sunshine.', 'A half bath with modern lighting and single vanity can also be found downstairs.', 'Upstairs you will find newer carpets and a bonus loft/den area, perfect for a second living space or home office.', "The sumptuous master suite is bright and airy and comes complete with a private balcony with views of the Mediterranean-style community and it's lush landscaping and palm trees, two walk-in closets, seating area and luxurious bathroom with countless upgrades including jacuzzi tub, glass-screened rainfall shower, custom dual vanity, separate toilet and crystal lighting fixtures.", 'The second bathroom is just as inviting with glass-screened combo tub/shower, single vanity and mirror with modern LED backlighting.', 'Both the second and third bedrooms also have newer carpets, ample closet space and updated lighting fixtures.', 'Coastal Bay is located conveniently directly off US1.', 'This gated neighborhood features beautiful landscaping, pool, jacuzzi as well as two-story clubhouse with fitness centre, social room, kitchen and lobby.', 'Residents of Coastal Bay are at the center of it all just minutes from the beach, Intracoastal waterway, Downtown Delray and Atlantic Avenue, a wide array of supermarkets, retail shops, casual and fine dining restaurants, public parks, community events and more.', 'Schedule a showing today!']
